visual.name: processMiningProcessMap
visual.description: Power Automate Process Mining Process Map allows users to visualize a process in a graphical way that can be used to find inefficiencies and areas of improvement for a process. The visual allows the user to select different metrics, provides filtering capabilities and integrates with other Power BI visuals.
